verbose_text: Pre-exercise NEFA concentration increased significantly following HF (from 0.39 +/- 0.08 to 0.61 +/- 0.08 mmol/L) and decreased significantly after eating HGI (from 0.44 +/- 0.09 to 0.13 +/- 0.02 mmol/L) and LGI (from 0.55 +/- 0.08 to 0.27 +/- 0.07 mmol/L).
evidence: NEFA concentration increased significantly following HF
